IPHawk: A Puppet module for configuring IPHawk
==============================================

This is the iphawk module. IPHawk a simple IP monitoring utility.
This module configures Nginx, Mysql, and PHP appropriately for use with IpHawk.

IPHawk can be found here:
 * http://iphawk.sourceforge.net/

